## Description {#details}

Machine <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/type">Type</a>.

Every type that is supported natively by some processor targeted by LLVM occurs here. This means that any legal value type can be represented by an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mvt">MVT</a>.

Definition at line 35 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegentypes/machinevaluetype-h">MachineValueType.h</a>.
